title: Megabyte Punch GOG
description:
[img]http://img.sceper.eu/images/QCrLG.jpg[/img]

Build your own fighter. Replace your arms, legs, head and more with the limbs of your defeated enemies. 
Up to 4 player local co-op split screen and versus mode. 
150 collectable parts, 30 hidden colors and 6 unique electro-worlds with boss fights. 
Compatible with Windows XP, Vista, 7, 8.1

just install and play
